comments:
(Denoting shape) Word starting with:Zet=star Gaf=5-armed shape Bov=pentagon Wop=circle

(Denoting colour) Word endings: -isa=grey -ifa=yellow --xao=blue, sometimes red  sho=sometimes red

  I tried to ascertain/learn this from observing the pictures and correct answer (observing the pattern), gaining confidence in the meanings over time. I didn't write anything down.

  It was quite easy to learn the first part of the words (denoting shape), but learning the word endings (denoting colour) was harder, especially the endings for 'red' and 'blue' which seemed to vary depending on shape (unlike 'grey' and 'yellow').
